      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_09d1b52c-b31a-4d2d-a0c2-24b851f17d43" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Students can <a href="https://community.canvaslms.com/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-view-the-rubric-for-a-quiz/ta-p/453" target="_blank">view the rubric for the quiz on the Submission Details page</a>, which is accessible from the Grades page.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
